XHTML_elements_reference_stylesheet_template.html

A Free HTML XHTML styleguide template with common HTML and XHTML elements. Use case 1: Attach stylesheets to this document to ensure you've styled all of a project's common elements. Use case 2: Leave a copy on the site's server for the next person to use as a 'look-book' or 'style-guide' for the site. Use case 3: Use it to copy and paste in common elements like forms and table data when creating markup for a site. Use case 4+: Whatever you find it useful for. Enjoy!" 


Feel free to edit, update, and generally improve this document any way you see fit. 

Best, 

F

